      "description": "This initial release includes the following key features:\r\n\r\n- Rendering Markdown notes into HTML based on specific (customizable) CSS\r\n\r\n- One-click copying of the rendered HTML page into rich text\r\n\r\n- One-click synchronization of the rendered HTML page to the WeChat Official Account's drafts folder\r\n\r\n- Automatic uploading of images from articles to the WeChat Official Account's resource library",
